Enroute Lace Up Price: Rs.2199

Impress your colleagues on your first day at office by donning this classic pair of shoes from the house of Enroute. These brown formal shoes have neat panel and stitch details that can boost your confidence and heighten your style. The soft footbeds of these lace-up shoes can offer you comfort throughout the day. Wear these shoes and experience a relaxed and comfortable walk. Pair these Enroute Lace Up Shoes with a classy formal shirt and a well-tailored formal trousers to get a perfect office attire.
